From 9245ec1be1b7fcfc481c8f7cf5877abe7294e4da Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kimi Claw <admin@digitatal.ru>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 07:53:33 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Hotfix 4.0.1: Critical fixes for production deployment

Database:
- Added missing columns to communications table
- Updated users_role_check constraint for new roles
- Added Milestone and MilestoneSubmission models

Bot:
- Fixed start.py FSMContext parameter
- Added SUBMIT_DESCRIPTION constant
- Removed emojis for Python compatibility
- Fixed scheduler imports
- Simplified mass messaging UI

API:
- Fixed bot-generate-code endpoint URL
- Added UUID validation in Files API

AI:
- Enabled Cerebras provider for teacher reviews
- Disabled public AI providers
- Removed AI mention from help text

Config:
- Added YANDEX_DISK_TOKEN
- Added CEREBRAS_API_KEY

See CHANGELOG.md for full details
